title: You Are Never Too Far Gone
description:
Sadie speaks with singer and author Kelsey Grimm about the dangers of looking for your identity in another person and the one place you will find your true identity. Making small concessions for other people can quickly change who you are, and not dealing with your past can wreck your future. No matter what, you are never too far from God, and you are always loved by him. Kelsey's book, "Over It," is available now.
